=== STELLAR_MAP ===
# id: 2
# title: The Stellar Map
# chinese_title: 星图
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

A holographic projector flickers to life as you pass, painting the air with constellations you don't recognize. The star map shows routes through sectors long thought impassable. Ancient navigational data streams across the display in both Standard and an unknown script.

* [Download the star chart data]
  ~ gain_radical("星")
  "星" (xīng) — star, celestial body
* [Study the unknown script]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "学" (xué) — to study, to learn
* [Cross-reference with known charts]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "比" (bǐ) — to compare
